{"tid":1628511,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽]對家開始分化 呢家更加要大大力裝修","createTime":"2019-10-06T03:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T04:57:14.000Z","uid":92477,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"20a030e0ef4acfb912027a36014b0b448d3da32b","tid":1628511,"uid":92477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L9j2f9A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL9j2f9A.jpg&h=b72183ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢家各區既裝修行動就係要大大聲同林鄭講<br />\n你所謂既救火<br />\n係用緊火水救火<br />\n<br />\n香港人係唔會驚架<br />\n<br />\n裝修影響越大就代表佢既決策錯誤就越大<br />\n<br />\n失民意?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拿 對家開始分化<br />\n民意一早已經歸哂邊<br />\n明事理既會屌沿頭即林鄭<br />\n藍絲就繼續暴徒前暴徒後<br />\n<br />\n呢家個景況係特區政府一手一腳造成<br />\n只係官逼民反<br />\n<br />\n行動大規模升級既時間點係政府繞過立法會<br />\n強制立蒙面法後<br />\n對國際同香港輿論<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所有責任同沿頭都只會係政府到</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以呢家更加要大大力裝修<br />\n要以黨鐵為首"},{"pid":"876beb1292ba94e8b9a2fb00a3524655fe2f3a04","tid":1628511,"uid":92477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:20:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c8f860cf16dc2d93077d4de7eb3f587437ec5dc","tid":1628511,"uid":92477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:23:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76b16eae3cebe37511fcc3f0cb0af17f4ce35d1c","tid":1628511,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:24:31.000Z","msg":"[裝修師傅入] 唔好亂接Job，入嚟睇吓我條List<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1623406\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1623406</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f8e29dcbc02895da53dcc7e5175ecc82328e41ad","tid":1628511,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:24:55.000Z","msg":"有一種方法可團結全港九成市民<br />\n<a 